            img(src='public/static/alien.png' alt='Alien' width='80' height='108')
            hr
            h2 FAQ
            h3 Is it really true that you are a professional web developer?
            p Yes.
            h3 But how is that possible?
            p I have completed training as a professional web designer
            h3 Ah no, I mean because this website looks shitty
            p
                | I beg you pardon?
                img(src='public/static/angry_alien.png' alt='Angry alien' width='60' height='70' style='width: 30px; height: 35px')
