            p.
                Maybe it doesn&apos;t look the best but at least it loads faster than your jQuery bloated page.
                Aaaaand it&apos;s for sure easy to maintain. Aaaaand maybe I was just too lazy to actually do something
                pretty.
            h3 Do all your websites look like this?
            p Not all, there are actual some real ones
            h3 Like?
            p
                | For example
                a(href='https://www.myzivi.ch' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer nofollow') MyZivi
                | and a lot of other projects I did @Renuo
            h3 You&apos;re only doing websites or do you have other skills as well?
            p.
                Some, yes. Mainly involving backend stuff, iOS programming, photographing
                and pretending to be busy.
